id=live_wallpaper_keeper
name=Live Wallpaper Keeper
version=v1.0.0
versionCode=1
author=KingAether
description=Keeps your live wallpaper from reverting to default after reboot. Backs up wallpaper_info.xml when the wallpaper is healthy and restores it at boot if it reverted, then reloads the wallpaper service.
